In a scenario where bandwidth, delay, jitter and bit error rate are evenly set up, we take α = β = γ = δ = 1/4. However, many conceivable scenarios can be patterned by conveniently assessing α, β, γ and δ.
At this step, each cell is scored and in UE side, while roaming between cells, the selection can be made by choosing the nearest cell with minimum score.

