diﬀers. For example, MEW introduces relatively higher delay for conversational calls when using AHP weights and improved with the fuzzy achievement. Also, an increasing of gap between AHP and FAHP is noticed in VIKOR scheme; this latter is due to the drop of the performance of the AHP-VIKOR. Yet, VIKOR provides better delays in AHP and FAHP schemes comparing with the other methods.

