The delay in background traﬃc is displayed in ﬁgure 5.4. Clearly, VIKOR introduces the least delays in both AHP and FAHP versions. MEW and TOPSIS Schemes induce relatively the same delays with a narrow improvement when using FAHP, while the delay in SAW algorithm declines considerably and provides the highest delay.

